PDF Creation and Scanning Tips for ECF PDF Creation and Scanning Tips for ECF Please keep the pdf file size under 5MB The steps below will help you achieve this PDF Creation Recommendations 1 Use Adobe Acrobat 5 PDF Writer to convert your wordperfect or MS Word documents to PDF 2 Try to stick with normal fonts or default fonts in wordperfect or word such as courier and times new roman Unusual fonts can sometimes create a problem for Adobe Scanner Recommendations 1 Please scan only in black and white 2 Set your scanner resolution preferably to 250 DPI Do not scan higher than 300 DPI 
